<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<databaseChangeLog xmlns="http://www.liquibase.org/xml/ns/dbchangelog" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.liquibase.org/xml/ns/dbchangelog-ext http://www.liquibase.org/xml/ns/dbchangelog/dbchangelog-ext.xsd http://www.liquibase.org/xml/ns/dbchangelog http://www.liquibase.org/xml/ns/dbchangelog/dbchangelog-latest.xsd">

    <!--
        Liquibase generateChangeLog orqali (bo'sh DB va haqiqiy dev DB
        isemid2 orasidagi farqdan) avtomatik yaratildi.

        Sabab: Card/Act/Patient modullari va IAM bazaviy jadvallari (users,
        organization, role, permission va bog'lovchi jadvallar) hech qachon
        Liquibase orqali emas, balki ddl-auto=update orqali yaratilgan edi —
        shu sababli ular uchun hech qanday changelog fayli yo'q edi. Mavjud
        9 ta qo'lda yozilgan fayl allaqachon qamrab olgan jadvallar
        (ref_country, ref_region, ref_district, ref_neighborhood, form058,
        fm058_location, form058_1, form058_1_other_injured_person,
        system_settings) bu fayldan ataylab chiqarib tashlangan.

        catalogName/schemaName atributlari olib tashlandi (avtomatik
        generatsiya paytida joriy DB nomi bilan qattiq bog'langan edi) — bu
        fayl istalgan nomdagi DB'ga qarshi portable bo'lishi uchun.

        Card/Act jadvallari BU FAYLDA YO'Q — ular form058'ga FK orqali
        bog'liq (masalan card.form058_id), shuning uchun alohida
        `changelog/zzz-card-act/` papkasiga chiqarilgan — u alifbo bo'yicha
        "form058"/"form0581" papkalaridan KEYIN ishga tushishi kerak
        (`includeAll` papkalarni alifbo tartibida o'qiydi), aks holda
        "relation form058 does not exist" xatosi bilan barbod bo'ladi.
    -->

